    <h1> Taiwan is an underrated travel destination! </h1>
      <p> 
        Taiwan can be considered both South East Asia and East Asia depending on who you talk to. Big things come in small packages and the same can be said for the Republic of China! Taiwan has so much to offer on this small island, why would you go anywhere else?         
      </p>

    <h2>Packages </h2>
      <p> 
        From foodie tours, diving resorts to historical monuments, there is a little bit of something for every type of traveller! Take a look at our tour packages below:
